Package uk.ac.bris.cs.scotlandyard.model

Class ImmutableBoard

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.bris.cs.scotlandyard.model.ImmutableBoard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Board
    public final class ImmutableBoard
extends Object
implements Board, Serializable
    A POJO representing an immutable game board. This is useful for snapshotting or serialising game states.
    NOTE: This class isn't really intended for use with the cw-model part but if you can justify the use then feel free to include it.
